{"id": "1445902154022916116", "channel_id": "1445902154022916116", "author_id": "258062995110756352", "author_name": "kezrin", "content": "Make an early Phase in Mission Report dedicated to forcing players to utilize realm mechanics. New players coming into the game very often don't learn about realm mechanics like Crimson Furnace or Tentacle stance switching until very later on, like chapter 8 of arc 1. This would incentivize players to look into the realms and actually learn about it instead of going through the entirety of arc 2 without realizing that red stance causes tentacles to attack with every damage instance. The quests could be:\n\n1. Use Crimson Furnace to heal X HP\n2. Switch tentacle stances to Tranquil Sea and Raging Waves\n3. Use Raging Waves stance to trigger X tentacle attacks before the end of the turn\n4. Use Annihilation to take X cards out of Ultra Space", "timestamp": "2025-12-03T22:18:57.082000+00:00", "thread_id": "1445902154022916116", "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1445902154391883979", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2032933, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1445902154022916116/1445902154391883979/image.png?ex=69cc4851&is=69caf6d1&hm=3ded5b9b66c987213c7b13476a1d333676b5a4cad32edfc864626a4fb32a8585&"}]}
